description: List all assets ( DASHBOARD, ANALYSIS, and DATASET) in a folder.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID for the Amazon Web Services account that contains the folder.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.

nested_items.name: FolderMemberList
nested_items.description: A structure that contains all of the folder members (dashboards, analyses, and datasets) in the folder.

nested_items.name: MemberArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the member.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token for the next set of results, or null if there are no more results.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.
